{"tid":1470802,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"運動已經去到新一頁","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T11:46:20.000Z","uid":201178,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fe03965f784c339384d2fdd22f817204f03601d7","tid":1470802,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:41:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">就係已經去到國際層面，中共都已經擺到明認真對付我地！</span></strong><br />\n由琴日件大伏到今日內地傳媒同KOL天衣無縫既配合，就知中共開始打輿論戰！<br />\n再睇返呢埋佢地咁怕我地傳訊息返大陸，就證明我地既運動已經一步步影響緊內地，<br />\n有影響中共管治危機。<br />\n<br />\n不過，個影響仲係好係，但我地唔會比佢地。<br />\n請開始內地文宣戰線，用真誠一步步打倒兩地的火牆。<br />\n我地對手唔係中國，而係極權！<br />\n馬上開始輿論戰！"},{"pid":"e46fe0302fe2446688f8131a3e637cce5bea3319","tid":1470802,"uid":28155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:43:59.000Z","msg":"不過，個影響仲係好係，但我地唔會比佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇左十次都唔明"},{"pid":"2cd992b9d585026b677704febb77614d402d477c","tid":1470802,"uid":33645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45e66f4db82a4e9aeb81c13c4a3e4fe2bb7ffa5","tid":1470802,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:44:28.000Z","msg":"而家係用文宣打仗<br />\n唔係用不合作同勇武<br />\n<br />\n做呢啲<br />\n自己又有機會犯錯<br />\n又有樣會送頭<br />\n<br />\n有乜謂<br />\n國際已有足夠子彈唔使再做更多粒"},{"pid":"cab0ec9a9eea71179fd48d214edebb15587ca147","tid":1470802,"uid":201178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e46fe0302fe2446688f8131a3e637cce5bea3319","tid":1470802,"uid":28155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:43:59.000Z","msg":"不過，個影響仲係好係，但我地唔會比佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇左十次都唔明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:44:50.000Z","msg":"不過，個影響仲係好細，但我地唔會比佢停。<br />\nSORRY手快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e881b3eaacc9edcf7a2c0f80b0447888e7f052","tid":1470802,"uid":237275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c